title: Impossibly Easy Chicken Pot Pie
directions: Heat oven to 400ºF. Mix vegetables, chicken and soup in ungreased glass pie plate, 9x1 1/4 inches.
Stir together remaining ingredients with fork until blended. Pour into pie plate.
Bake 30 minutes or until golden brown.
ingredients: 1 2/3 cups Green Giant™ Steamers™ frozen mixed vegetables
1 can (10 3/4 ounces) condensed cream of chicken soup
